{"tid":2441625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國vs納粹：不只是反伊斯蘭，而且是文化滅絕回族","createTime":"2021-03-10T23:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T00:07:15.000Z","uid":334191,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4b5034aa5b914d82ea0e755b1207d2a7011ebb","tid":2441625,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T23:19:12.000Z","msg":"我和伊斯梅爾&middot;馬聚作客自由亞洲，討論中國對回族的文化滅絕：<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;伊斯蘭之於回族具有宗教和文化的二重性，這正如猶太教之於猶太人。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;中國破壞清真飲食和清真寺，正如納粹摧殘猶太飲食和猶太會堂。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;中國和納粹不僅針對目標族群中多數人的信仰，也針對族群文化本身。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;消滅民族文化，符合《防止及懲治滅絕種族罪公約》對種族滅絕的定義。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;中國對回族的防範、削弱、滲透和清洗，是中共建政以來的傳統。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我年輕時的&rdquo;政策寬松期&ldquo;曾入寺學習，也曾經歷過警察破門而入。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;極權主義的政教合一性無法容忍非官方信仰，總體控制性無法容忍社會自組織。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;當局壓制&rdquo;蠻夷&ldquo;和&ldquo;外來文化&ldquo;,也是為了獲得中華民族主義的加持。<br />\n<br />\n全文及語音（10分鐘）<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shaoshuminzu/wy-03102021104230.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fshaoshuminzu%2Fwy-03102021104230.html&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPlFFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=52f9bc5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shaoshuminzu/wy-03102021104230.html</a><br />\n注：可惜與納粹比較的部分在整理時未獲保留；另外我當時說的是&rdquo;東突厥斯坦&ldquo;，不是&rdquo;新疆&ldquo;。"},{"pid":"5ecdbf64df7bbada3d3413acd30f97c1b7a05bc9","tid":2441625,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"南蒙古都走唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.newtalk.tw/resize_action2/600/album/news/460/5f4f502e17918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.newtalk.tw%2Fresize_action2%2F600%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F460%2F5f4f502e17918.jpg&h=ff273d82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d87urpdhi5rdo.cloudfront.net/09-05-2020/t_c465432b085c4cfb90ee7f21314012b2_name_